Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\bord5\fs80\fn@方正兰亭圆_GBK_粗\pos(113.067,291.467)\frz296.2\c&H282E39&\3c&HE3EBF3&}嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_粗\c&H4A5052&\pos(1492.8,949.6)}拚命將鼻子伸長
