Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:02:02.85,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H000000&\3c&H0000B6&}I feel my soul rise  like a scream crawling up my spine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:12.37,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For his sake alone  no doubt I would cross every single line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:20.74,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}There's no retreat  no mercy and no breath to spare  it's fair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:27.33,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You touched what's mine  so I'll be waiting for you there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:35.09,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The system is cracked  my calm was just outer shell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:43.10,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Override complete  welcome to my private hell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.24,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No one can stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:52.82,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm unbound  unbroken  you should beware
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:03:00.66,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm unbound  unbroken  beware
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.31,0:02:02.85,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}靈魂在升騰  如吶喊順著脊梁攀上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.41,0:02:12.37,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只為他一人  我定會越過所有界疆
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.10,0:02:20.74,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沒有退讓  沒有憐憫  不給喘息一秒  公平較量
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.00,0:02:27.33,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你既染指我物  我必在彼處候場
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.88,0:02:35.09,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}系統已崩壞  我的冷靜只是徒有虛表
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.54,0:02:43.10,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}覆寫已完成  歡迎來到我的私人地獄
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.24,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}此刻我無人能擋
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.85,0:02:52.82,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再拘束  不再受傷  可別怪我沒給你警告
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.58,0:03:00.66,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再拘束  不再受傷  別怪我沒警告
